com.tractrac.model.lib.api.event

Interface ICompetitorClass

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttachable, IIdentifiable, INamed, com.tractrac.util.lib.api.serialize.ISerializable

    public interface ICompetitorClass
extends INamed, com.tractrac.util.lib.api.serialize.ISerializable

    Encapsulates data related to a Competitor Class in an Event.

    All Competitors of an Event are typically divided into groups or classes. An instance of a Competitor Class can be used to represent data related to such a group/class.

    An instance of this class has a unique id and a name. Custom data may be attached to each Competitor Class instance.

    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Jesper Grooss
